{"tid":2034814,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【騰訊股價】騰訊5億入股《牧場物語》日本遊戲公司Marvelous 成最大股東","createTime":"2020-05-25T12:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T00:06:55.000Z","uid":85180,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"64f70db9fe3bb7a19e63196e8790b8d6d358124c","tid":2034814,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:59:51.000Z","msg":"【騰訊股價】騰訊5億入股《牧場物語》日本遊戲公司Marvelous 成最大股東<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2650000/2652214/20200525_TEN_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2650000%2F2652214%2F20200525_TEN_1024.jpg&h=d5cde64d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 騰訊據報以逾5億元總代價，購日本遊戲公司Marvelous 20%股權。<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，騰訊 （00700） 將透過全資附屬公司Image Frame Investment，收購日本遊戲開發商Marvelous 20%股權，初步估算總代價或逾5億港元。交易完成後，騰訊將成為Marvelous最大股東。<br />\n<br />\nMarvelous會以每股576日圓（約41.5港元），向騰訊發行862萬股新股；同時Marvelou股東Amuse Capital、Sega遊戲公司創辦人中山隼雄（Nakayama Hayao）將以相同價格，分別向騰訊出售283萬、70.86萬股Marvelous股份。<br />\n<br />\nMarvelous旗下熱門遊戲包括《牧場物語》、《機甲戰魔》，事實上，騰訊去年已宣布與Marvelous合作打造《牧場物語》系列手機遊戲《牧場物語OL》。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊今日收報416.6元，升1%，成交82億元。"},{"pid":"9658bd631f90e82e8f07d67822fa0d5ce1cac3e1","tid":2034814,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:29:34.000Z","msg":"童年回憶淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41fb302bd190d99c6f49df4b0b474716a05636f","tid":2034814,"uid":258770,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJoQLYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJoQLYr.jpg&h=91cae18d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54b4fc0dca0b05814ac622249dd9abcc70e7aa1e","tid":2034814,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"SEGA 賣仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse